293
00:17:53,776 --> 00:17:55,876
Kenapa mereka tidak menjawabnya, ya?

294
00:17:55,876 --> 00:17:58,576
Mungkin karena putus asa mencari kucing,

295
00:17:58,576 --> 00:18:00,076
