358
00:21:09,676 --> 00:21:12,176
Tapi mereka seharusnya mengatakan langsung,

359
00:21:12,176 --> 00:21:14,476
"Itu kucing tuan kami. Jadi kalau kau sudah mengambilnya,

360
00:21:14,476 --> 00:21:16,476
